name: dpShowLatency
tagline: A Mozilla Firefox add-on for analyzing IBM DataPower latency log entries.
body:
# Firefox Add-on: DataPower Latency Record Analyzer

This Firefox Add-on is relevant to users of 
[IBM DataPower appliances](http://www-03.ibm.com/software/products/en/datapower-xi52).
It provides an analysis tool for latency records written to the 
DataPower Web UI log viewer.  This add-on is basically an automation
of the copy-n-paste task needed to use the
[Show Latency](http://glezen.org/ShowLatency.html) page.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
